ea": {"text": "多地中小银行密集调降存款利率，为何出现存款利率「调降潮」？国有四大行会降低存款利率吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "4 月以来，广东、湖北、陕西、河南等多个省份的中小银行纷纷发布公告，下调人民币存款挂牌利率，涉及活期存款、定期存款、大额存单等，不同期限调整幅度不同。 接受《经济参考报》采访的专家表示，去年以来，在市场利率总体有所下行的背景下，国有大型银行和部分股份制银行纷纷下调存款利率，此次调整可视为中小银行的「跟进」，是其为压低负债成本所作的市场化定价行为。专家提示，未来存款利率仍存在下行空间，广大居民可根据个人需求，衡量收益与风险的关系，进行多元化资产配置。中小银行存款利率集体「补降」 未来或进一步下行 _ 经济参考网 _ 新华社《经济参考报》官方网站"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-28d9c4536905ba01b9ff9e881cc34eb1_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "62 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/597096718"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI0Ljy+J/yvblPEAMaCDk0OTY4OTM5IK6hjaIGMAM4tQJAE3IJNTk3MDk2NzE4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1682237224.8653705", "card_id": "Q_596349464", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 28}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "在什么时候音乐最治愈你？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-13b22cc4934e772218195458d0f2a2c2_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "61 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596349464"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I0Ljy+J/yvblPEAMaCDk0ODAzMjUyIJPX+aEGMAA4KkAUcgk1OTYzNDk0NjR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1682237224.8662546", "card_id": "Q_596480125", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 51}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "哪一首歌陪伴了你最多难眠的夜晚？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b09f3c264374821ce5878a9fc7410f25_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "60 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {